hed>2023-10-11T13:52:53-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-11T13:52:53-04:00</updated><title>微软已经堵住了免费的Windows 11漏洞——Windows 7按键不再起作用</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木桌上的 Surface Laptop Go 3&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OVItS_ucFVdtZAPAVsdOzWg_LU8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72745279/236820_Surface_Laptop_Go_3_AKrales_0028.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;QpEDTM&quot;>;微软现在正在阻止 Windows 7 和 Windows 8 密钥无法激活 Windows 11 的副本。&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/1/14/21065140/how-to-upgrade-microsoft-windows 这是一个漏洞-7-10-free-os&quot;>;已经存在多年&lt;/a>;，允许人们免费从 Windows 7 或 8 升级到 Windows 10 或 11。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;w08XBi&quot;>;Microsoft最初宣布了阻止 Windows 11 中的 Windows 7 和 Windows 8 密钥的更改 &lt;a href=&quot;https://devicepartner.microsoft.com/en-us/communications/comm-windows-ends-installation-path-for-free- windows-7-8-upgrade?ranMID=24542&amp;amp;ranEAID=kXQk6*ivFEQ&amp;amp;ranSiteID=kXQk6.ivFEQ-98CvwoiQFutIMBr9nXcOFg&amp;amp;epi=kXQk6.ivFEQ-98CvwoiQFutIMBr9nXcOFg&amp;amp;irgwc=1&amp;amp;OCID=AIDc mm549zy227_aff_7593_1243925&amp;amp;tduid=%28ir__ljdpmt6yv0kf6xmlzg20m1oqru2xbyycpmflj2xi00%29%287593 %29%281243925%29%28kXQk6.ivFEQ-98CvwoiQFutIMBr9nXcOFg%29%28%29&amp;amp;irclickid=_ljdpmt6yv0kf6xmlzg20m1oqru2xbyycpmflj2xi00&quot;>;上个月末&lt;/a>;，但当时，我们看到密钥仍在激活，并且它不是明确该禁令何时真正生效。微软向 The Verge 证实，截至本周，Windows 7 密钥现已完全禁止全新安装 Windows 11。 &lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;Tom Warren / The Verge 的屏幕截图&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Windows 11 将不再激活 Windows 7 密钥。&lt;/em>;&lt; /figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;T5OZRL&quot;>;我已经在干净的环境中测试了多个 Windows 7 按键...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2023/10/11/23913107/microsoft-windows-11-block-windows-7-8-keys-upgrade-activation&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913107/microsoft-windows-11-block-windows-7-8-keys-upgrade-activation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913107/microsoft-windows-11-block-windows-7-8-keys-upgrade-activation</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-11T13:10:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-11T13:10:00-04:00</updated><title> Anker 的 bassy Sport X10 耳机在 Prime Day 折扣近 40%</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Soundcore Sport X10 耳塞在重物旁边的图像。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/oWVy-IF-wMlkdkM2hF0khdn-iag=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72745091/DSCF0068。 0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;与其他 Anker 产品一样，Sport X10 以经济实惠的价格提供可靠的性能而闻名。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;MrpslN&quot;>;如果您厌倦了在跑步机上跑步或锻炼时耳机总是掉落，那么可能是时候了最后投资一些适合锻炼的音频。这就是 Anker 的 Soundcore Sport X10 的用武之地，它是我们最喜欢的无线耳机之一。可旋转入耳式耳机通常售价 69.99 美元，目前 &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/dp/B09WMJCQRM?tag= theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;作为零售商 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23903764/amazon 的一部分，在亚马逊获得折扣待遇&lt;/a>; -october-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2023&quot;>;秋季 Prime Day 活动&lt;/a>;，价格降至历史最低价 51.99 美元（折扣 18 美元）。&lt;/p>; &lt; div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;Ersm7v&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[ {&quot;title&quot;:&quot;十月 Prime 会员日第 2 天最佳优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23912000/prime-day-best-deals-tech -earbuds-gaming-amazon-october&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您现在可以购买的最佳健身耳机&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23413809/best-workout-fitness -running-earbuds&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;黄金日最佳耳塞和耳机优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23910368/amazon-october-prime-day-best- 